  h1 msrd
    span .io

  p.slug microsoft regional directors 

  :markdown
    The Microsoft Regional Director program has a new logo. In keeping with the 
    spirit of Microsoft's 2012 corporate and product line rebranding, the RD 
    logo was refashioned to reflect their new design asthetic:
    
    - Monochromatic
    - Segoe typeface
    - Simple layout and icon
    - Semantic HTML

  h2 The Logo
  p.
    There are three sizes of images (all PNGs) to choose from, with each size
    coming in 2 flavors: white background and transparent background.

  ul
    li 336 x 96 pixels
    li 672 x 192 pixels
    li 1344 x 384 pixels

  h3 Small

  figure
    a(href='/logo/msrd-logo-96px.png')
      img(src='/logo/msrd-logo-96px.png', alt='logo 96 pixels', width=336, height=96)
    figcaption 336x96 px png

  figure
